# Ignore all knowledge folders
00_Inbox/
10_Journal/
20_My-knowledge/
30_Library/
40_Project-papers/

# Ignore Obsidian workspace settings (usually machine-specific)
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/backlink.json
.obsidian/graph.json
.obsidian/page-preview.json
.obsidian/core-plugins.json (optional, but often kept)

# Ignore media and deleted files
90_System/Attachments/
90_System/Archive/
.trash/

# Keep system configuration and templates
!90_System/
!90_System/Templates/
!90_System/Templates/*.md
!90_System/SEVERAL GOOD GITHUB.md

# Keep the instruction manual
GEMINI.md
